PN,31902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1780164666
OL,3,CLabour refers Nigel Farage's Russia
OL,4,Cphone hack claim to police
OL,6,FLabour's chairwoman, Anna Turley, gave
OL,7,FFarage 24 hours on Wednesday to
OL,8,Fpublicly confirm that he or Reform UK
OL,9,Fhad reported their claims of hostile
OL,10,Fstate activity by Russia to the
OL,11,Frelevant authorities.
OL,13,FLabour said Reform has failed to
OL,14,Fconfirm whether they reported the hack
OL,15,Fand that "it remains unclear what
OL,16,Fproactive action they have taken".
OL,18,FTurley said she has since referred the
OL,19,Fallegations to the National Cyber
OL,20,FSecurity Centre (NCSC) and the
OL,21,FMetropolitan Police.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
