OL,3,CLabour refers Nigel Farage's Russia
OL,4,Cphone hack claim to police
OL,6,FITV News understands that Reform UK
OL,7,Fhas reported the alleged hack to the
OL,8,Frelevant authorities.
OL,10,FA party source said: "Labour are on
OL,11,Fthe ropes and they're just playing
OL,12,Fgames."
OL,14,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,15,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,16,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,17,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
