PN,31904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1780164666
OL,3,CLabour refers Nigel Farage's Russia
OL,4,Cphone hack claim to police
OL,6,FIn her original letter to Farage,
OL,7,FTurley outlined her concerns, saying:
OL,8,F"This would constitute a serious
OL,9,Fcybercrime and a potential hostile-
OL,10,Fstate operation directed at the leader
OL,11,Fof a British political party."
OL,13,FFollowing Labour's report to the
OL,14,Fauthorities, Turley continued to
OL,15,Fstress the "wider implications for
OL,16,FBritain's national security" and
OL,17,Fpolitical integrity.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
