PN,31905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1780164666
OL,3,CLabour refers Nigel Farage's Russia
OL,4,Cphone hack claim to police
OL,6,FAlthough the NCSC could not confirm
OL,7,Fwhether Reform reported the suspected
OL,8,Fattack, it said it stands "ready to
OL,9,Fsupport with any suspected cyber
OL,10,Fincident that is reported to us".
OL,12,FIt added: "Defending democracy is
OL,13,Falways our priority and we provide a
OL,14,Frange of expert guidance, support and
OL,15,Factive cyber defence services to help
OL,16,Fprotect individuals from online
OL,17,Fattacks."
